name: the many faces of Schwarzenegger: conan and grace
description: in 1984's Conan the Destroyer, Strangé and arnold schwarzenegger set out on a quest to escort Queen Taramisu's virgin niece, Jehnna, to restor the jeweled horn of the dreaming god Dagoth in exchange for the resurrection of Conan's true love Valeria.. Along the way, Conan saves Strangé from a mob of villagers and -- in debt to him -- joins him on his quest. Here, the actor Strangé, known in real life as Grace Jones, hyperrealistically strangles Conan with a bow staff. But, in the historical film, which is mild for sex and nudity, moderate for violence and gore, mild for alcohol/drugs/smoking and moderate for frightening/intense scenes, the two are on the same team!
